to better equip your raiding force and to do harder mobs faster, council or dkp is the best way, anything that involves /randoms is flawed, because of the inherent nature of randomness. <p><img src=http://ickhor.homestead.com/files/verymean.gif><br><font face="Arial" size=2 color=#FFFFFF><b><TABLE STYLE="filter:GLOW(color=blue,strength=#+2)"  ><font color="#FFFFFF"><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=29047>Gear</a>*<a href=http://pub70.ezboard.com/bdracaena>Drac</a>*<a href=mailto:nihil@ijustdontcare.com>Mail</a>*<a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis>Brell</a></b>
